### ================= 用户模块测试 =================

### 1. 测试注册接口
POST http://localhost:8080/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test_user_001",
  "password": "123456",
  "checkPassword": "123456",
  "gender": 1
}

### 2. 测试登录接口 (注意：测试下面接口前，必须先点一次这个绿三角)
POST http://localhost:8080/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test_user_001",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. 测试获取当前登录用户
GET http://localhost:8080/user/current
Content-Type: application/json


### ================= 饮食记录模块测试 =================

### 4. 测试添加饮食记录
# 注意：前提是你的 food 表里必须有一条 id 为 1 的食物数据
POST http://localhost:8080/diet/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "foodId": 1,
  "mealType": 0,
  "quantity": 150.5,
  "recordDate": "2026-02-23"
}

### 5. 测试添加饮食记录（不传日期，测试默认当天的逻辑）
POST http://localhost:8080/diet/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "foodId": 1,
  "mealType": 1,
  "quantity": 200
}

### 6. 测试查询某天的饮食记录 (带日期参数)
GET http://localhost:8080/diet/daily?date=2026-02-23
Content-Type: application/json

### 7. 测试查询今天的饮食记录 (不带日期参数)
GET http://localhost:8080/diet/daily
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. 测试统计当日营养总摄入量
# 先执行登录，再执行这个
GET http://localhost:8080/diet/nutrition-stats?date=2026-02-23
Content-Type: application/json

### 9. 测试统计当日营养总摄入量
# 先执行登录，再执行这个
GET http://localhost:8080/diet/nutrition-stats
Content-Type: application/json